CbcParam: Extends CoinParam with Cbc-specific parameter codes.
Used by the standalone cbc-generic solver for command-line processing.

Parameter categories (CbcParamCode enum):
- Help: GENERALQUERY, HELP
- Action: BAB, IMPORT, EXPORT, PRINTSOL, READMIPSTART
- File: IMPORTFILE, EXPORTFILE, SOLUTIONFILE, MIPSTARTFILE
- Cut: GOMORYCUTS, MIRCUTS, PROBINGCUTS, KNAPSACKCUTS, etc.
- Heuristic: FPUMP, RINS, RENS, DIVINGC, GREEDY, etc.
- Boolean: CPX, DOHEURISTIC, SOS, USESOLUTION
- Keyword: STRATEGY, PREPROCESS, NODESTRATEGY, ORBITAL
- Integer: LOGLEVEL, THREADS, CUTDEPTH, MAXNODES, etc.
- Double: CUTOFF, ALLOWABLEGAP, TIMELIMIT, INCREMENT, etc.

Each parameter links to:
- parameters_: Parent CbcParameters collection
- model_: Associated CbcModel (for model parameters)
